Class ContestantInformation

java.lang.Object
  su.ContestantInformation
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class ContestantInformation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable

This class holds information for a contestant. It creates fields for first name, last name, street address (street number and street name), city, province, postal code, phone number and birth date.

Author:
Glen Su Nov 11 2015
